00:00.890 --> 00:03.480
<b>What? Another one surrendered without a fight?</b>

00:03.480 --> 00:06.730
<b>Honestly... How can they be so disloyal?</b>

00:06.730 --> 00:09.530
<b>Well, the viceroys in remote regions</b>

00:09.530 --> 00:15.110
<b>were those who were demoted for 
opposing the empire in the first place.</b>

00:15.110 --> 00:17.080
<b>It's no surprise that they would betray us.</b>

00:17.080 --> 00:20.660
<b>H-However, if this keeps up, 
the rebel army will reach the capitalâ€”</b>

00:20.660 --> 00:21.830
<b>Stop panicking.</b>

00:22.290 --> 00:24.500
<b>C-Commander-in-Chief Budo...</b>

00:24.500 --> 00:27.840
<b>They say the military should keep their mouths shut about politics.</b>

00:27.840 --> 00:32.340
<b>We've abided by that maxim for generations, 
but given the circumstances,</b>

00:32.340 --> 00:34.590
<b>I can't sit back and watch, Prime Minister.</b>

00:36.470 --> 00:37.850
<b>My, that's harsh.</b>

00:38.260 --> 00:40.140
<b>"Protect this nation."</b>

00:40.140 --> 00:44.770
<b>That is the mission that my family has 
been charged with for a thousand years.</b>

00:44.770 --> 00:49.860
<b>I shall suppress whatever disturbs the 
empire's peace with my own two hands,</b>

00:49.860 --> 00:51.940
<b>regardless of who or what it may be.</b>

00:51.940 --> 00:54.030
<b>Oh, how terrifying.</b>

00:54.030 --> 00:56.320
<b>But you need not worry.</b>

00:56.320 --> 01:01.040
<b>Even if the masses should rise up, 
we have countermeasures in place.</b>

01:01.490 --> 01:03.910
<b>Allow me to introduce you.</b>

01:04.250 --> 01:06.790
<b>In order to maintain public order within the empire,</b>

01:06.790 --> 01:09.960
<b>a new elite unit has been established!</b>

01:10.420 --> 01:12.380
<b>Sorry to intrude.</b>

01:15.630 --> 01:17.720
<b>He's not really cut out to be a commander,</b>

01:17.720 --> 01:22.020
<b>but I've chosen my son, Syura, for the job.</b>

01:22.020 --> 01:25.020
<b>Ah, so you're the famous Commander-in-Chief.</b>

01:25.480 --> 01:28.730
<b>I heard that only General Esdeath can match your strength.</b>

01:30.060 --> 01:34.650
<b>There's no need for someone of your rank to dirty his hands just because the peasants are revolting.{indeed they are}</b>

01:34.650 --> 01:36.780
<b>Leave it all to me.</b>

01:36.780 --> 01:38.490
<b>Oh? Where are you going?</b>

01:38.950 --> 01:45.830
<b>There are always a few rats that sniff around before the rest of the swarm arrives.</b>

01:45.830 --> 01:49.960
<b>Jeez. Can't he just take it easy for a change?</b>

01:50.290 --> 01:51.750
<b>Now, Syura...</b>

01:51.750 --> 01:54.710
<b>I'll be watching to see what you can do.</b>

01:54.710 --> 01:58.550
<b>Let's find out whether you're worthy to succeed me.</b>

01:58.550 --> 02:01.890
<b>I'll be sure to put on a show for you.</b>

